<ul>
<li>
<div><strong>How to join a text list.</strong> Each area of LifeWay operates their own text list.&#160;Visit the&#160;LifeWay.com area that interests you to see what opportunities are available.</div>
</li>

<li>
<div><strong>How to opt-out.&#160;</strong> No matter what text list you are part of, you can opt out anytime by texting the word "STOP" or "QUIT" to 32577 and you will be removed from our list.</div>
</li>

<li>
<div><strong>Where to get customer support.</strong> Support is available by texting the word "HELP" to 32577.</div>
</li>

<li>
<div><strong>Cost.</strong> Standard message rates apply.&#160;The only charges that are incurred are from your mobile service carrier.</div>
</li>

<li>

<div><strong>Participating carriers.</strong> ATT, Verizon, Sprint, Nextel, Boost, Dobson, Alltel, USCell and Suncom.</div>
</li>
</ul>
 
